, 應該做為公共圖書館服務的核心:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">刺激兒童及青少年的想像力及創造力。<br />\n讓表演藝術有演出的機會。<br />\n嘗試各種文化, 欣賞其間的差異。</span><br />\n<br />\n人地外國公共圖書館已經有地方俾人打機（PS4/X BOX 360），又有Creative Studio可以做剪片，玩音樂，做3D printing，Graphic design作品。甚至有地方可以借DVD/BLU-RAY睇電影同煲劇。小朋友又可以大聲玩。<br />\n<br />\n而且好多國家公共圖書館唔會規定禁止拍攝，外國好多圖書館都係instagrammable library。反而香港近幾年行回頭路嚴格禁止。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.adsttc.com/media/images/5dee/ff0a/3312/fd16/7900/0196/newsletter/Schmidt_Hammer_Lassen_Architects_State_Library_Victoria_10.jpg?1575943930\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.adsttc.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5dee%2Fff0a%2F3312%2Ffd16%2F7900%2F0196%2Fnewsletter%2FSchmidt_Hammer_Lassen_Architects_State_Library_Victoria_10.jpg%3F1575943930&h=4ff2b61f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.melbourne.vic.gov.au/SiteCollectionImages/dock-v3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.melbourne.vic.gov.au%2FSiteCollectionImages%2Fdock-v3.jpg&h=dee9e311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.melbourne.vic.gov.au/SiteCollectionImages/library-at-the-dock-terrace-668.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.melbourne.vic.gov.au%2FSiteCollectionImages%2Flibrary-at-the-dock-terrace-668.jpg&h=c00c6a87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://crosscut.com/sites/default/files/styles/max_2000x2000/public/images/articles/edwards_library_02_1.jpg?itok=8asApXOW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrosscut.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fmax_2000x2000%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Farticles%2Fedwards_library_02_1.jpg%3Fitok%3D8asApXOW&h=e6c8d355&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e268efc81237921cf9f9dfc9ddcdca43c0bf41ce","tid":2094503,"uid":199957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"反正嗰啲乜撚嘢國際人權組織言論自由同埋聯合國嗰班全部垃圾嚟嘅<br />\n中國而家好撚明顯係 我係唔跟你呀 吹咩反正你都吹我唔脹"},{"pid":"f05f0c8cf1c51bce709cf16f875824cf8689c1cd","